description:
Donations Paypal:
www.paypal.me/clarktracey1961 (Copy and paste)
Loosely based on the Radio 2 quiz show "Jazz Score", we present 6 weekly shows with a regular panel of British jazz musicians plus a special guest in each episode and it's chaired by Alyn Shipton.

You are encouraged to donate just £1 (or more if you're feeling particularly generous) to  paypal.me/clarktracey1961 (copy and paste) link, half of which will be passed on to the Macmillan Charity.
The regular panellists include Alan Barnes, Alex Garnett and Pete Long. This week's special guest is Iain Ballamy.

Like, subscribe and share to stay notified of our future Jazz Lockdown sessions!
